<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/28(Sat.) Do these countries hold the secret to a long and healthy life? &amp;  An earlier dinner may lower risk]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=192&amp;p=206#p206"><![CDATA[
Do these countries hold the secret to a long and healthy life?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2015/12/11/health/oldest-countries-secret-longer-life/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2015/12/11/heal ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Article 1 Discussions~~<br /><br />Q1) Why would a person want to live to be a centenarian or why not?<br />Q2)A healthy lifestyle isn’t just diet and exercise. So what is a healthy lifestyle? <br />Q3)From the context,  why those countries are outliving the rest -- and what secrets they hold to longer life?<br />Q4)How the strong family tie and stress-relieving cultural activities can increase life expectancy ?<br />Q5)what’s  your ideal plans of good diet, lifestyle, and health infrastructure for your older years<br /><br />Article 2 ~~~<br />Title :An earlier dinner may lower risk of some cancers, study says<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2018/07/17/health/eat-earlier-lower-cancer-risk-study/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/07/17/heal ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussions ~~~~<br />1)Please share  WHEN to eat  just as important as WHAT you eat.<br />2)Do you accept  eating  when your body tells you to, rather than eating out of habit<br />3)Do you get accustomed to eat more early, eat Less at night? share your comments!<br />4) Having you ever experienced night fasting really well affecting internal body  ?<br />5)Is it better to eat three meals a day or is it better to graze throughout the day?<br />6) Eating late at night might be generally disorder what kind digestive system of the body during the sleep?<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven, <br />板橋民生路二段237 號, <br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30, <br />minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Mon Jul 23, 2018 8:44 pm</p><hr />
